oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Warren C. Cox copyprint photograph
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Copyprint photograph of Pvt. Warren C. Cox, Co. I, 9th Ky. Inf. Regt., USA. Cox was born on October 30, 1838, in Smith County, Tennessee. He was the son of Duncan and Elizabeth Cox. Cox died on January 15, 1919, in Macon County, Tennessee. Cox wears an Army issued sack coat and a civilian hat.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Cox, Warren C.
